# mcmc-decryptor

A Python library for decrypting substitution ciphers using Metropolis sampling.

## Features

- Preprocess text
- Encrypt and decrypt substitution ciphers
- Optimize decryption using Metropolis sampling

## Installation

```bash
pip install mcmc_decryptor
